  schema:name "Law" ;
  schema:description "A LawfulClaim is a knowledge claim in the doubly quiescent position H* (both the historical record and every concurrent extension have closed on it). Neither past inquiry nor forward projection can push it further. The strongest epistemic position: grounded in history, present in every future." ;
